===Mandarin===
===Noun===
四字母詞 (''[[Pinyin]]'' sì zìmǔ cí)

# [[Tetragrammaton]]
# literal translation of [[four-letter word]]

====Usage notes====
This word is not commonly used.  A more colloquial way to say [[four-letter word]] would be [[三字經]].  This is because in Chinese, many swear words consist of three Chinese characters.

